HEADWORD: Sabianism
<hw>Sa"bi*an*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The doctrine of
the Sabians; the Sabian religion; that species of idolatry which
consists in worshiping the sun, moon, and stars; heliolatry.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>Sabaeanism</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

